OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FDurham schoolboy who wrote 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fto Ukraine president gets  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Freply                      
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A schoolboy has had a reply to a letter
OL,6, he sent to the President of Ukraine,   
OL,7, saying he was on the country's side.   
OL,9,FThomas, 12, a pupil at Durham Trinity  
OL,10,FSchool and Sports College popped a     
OL,11,Fhandwritten letter into a convoy of    
OL,12,Fsupplies collected by his classmates.  
OL,14,FAddressing it to "the best president"  
OL,15,FThomas told Volodymyr Zelensky he was  
OL,16,F"happy to be helping" Ukraine.         
OL,18,FDespite not expecting a reply, his     
OL,19,Fschool received one last week, saying  
OL,20,Fthe letter "brings a smile to my face".
